。他认为，断供短期内将对大陆的人工智能以及GPU相关企业带来一定的产能问题。不过，此次事件将进一步推动本土先进产能和良率爬坡，倒逼设备、材料等产业链加速完善。外媒：美国要求台积电停供大陆7纳米AI芯片"},"attached_info":"CkEIr+7C+p74xv1gEAMaCTExMTY4NjIyNyDU8ra5BjAAOLsCQBRyCjM1NDc2NTM0MzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9efb4b07bd1fcbbf1d6b001f828bf473_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1731399801.931631","card_id":"Q_270529364","target":{"id":270529364,"title":"四川成都有哪些值得一去的博物馆？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/270529364","type":"question","created":1522427511,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":122,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[398,411,1897],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ir+7C+p74xv1gEAMaCDIyMzkyNzM5IPfM+dUFMAA4ekAVcgkyNzA1MjkzNjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fa7e435aed1677a4d0de46f7069a20f8_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1731399801.931826","card_id":"Q_309598791","target":{"id":309598791,"title":"明兰最终为什么不选小公爷？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/309598791","type":"question","created":1547875059,"answer_count":186,"follower_count":342,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,1497,2102,8412,214508],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在盛明兰的心里还是有齐衡的，可为何最终却拒绝了他？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir+7C+p74xv1gEAMaCDMxMDc2NDY3IPPliuIFMAA41gJAFnIJMzA5NTk4NzkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f3f6ed0c059d33942